{"word":"Aaron","slug":"aaron","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Aaron</b> <a href=\"#/H175\">H175</a><br/><a href=\"#/G2\">G2</a> <br/> Lineage of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=20'>Exo 6:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=4'>Jos 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=21&verse=10'>Jos 21:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=3'>1Ch 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=13'>1Ch 23:13</a><br/> Marriage of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=23'>Exo 6:23</a><br/> Children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=23'>Exo 6:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=25'>Exo 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=3'>1Ch 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24&verse=2'>1Ch 24:2</a><br/> Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=23'>Exo 6:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=25'>Exo 6:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=15'>1Ch 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=53'>1Ch 6:53</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=24'>1Ch 24</a><br/> Meets Moses in the wilderness and is made spokesman for Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=16'>Exo 4:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=31'>Exo 4:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=2'>Exo 7:2</a><br/> Inspiration of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=1'>Exo 12:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=8'>Lev 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=1'>Lev 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=13&verse=1'>Lev 13:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=15&verse=1'>Lev 15:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=1'>Num 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=1'>Num 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=4&verse=17'>Num 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=1'>Num 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=19&verse=1'>Num 19:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=12'>Num 20:12</a><br/> Commissioned as a deliverer of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=13'>Exo 6:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=6&verse=27'>Exo 6:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=5'>Jos 24:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=12&verse=8'>1Sa 12:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=77&verse=20'>Psa 77:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=26'>Psa 105:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=6&verse=4'>Mic 6:4</a><br/> Summoned to Sinai with Nadab, Abihu, and seventy elders<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=24'>Exo 19:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=1'>Exo 24:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=10'>Exo 24:10</a><br/> Priesthood of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=1'>Exo 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=17&verse=13'>Num 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=1'>Num 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=99&verse=6'>Psa 99:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=5&verse=4'>Heb 5:4</a><br/> Consecration of, to the priesthood<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28'>Exo 28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8'>Lev 8</a><br/> Enters upon the priestly office<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9'>Lev 9</a><br/><a href='S:High Priest'>High Priest</a><br/> Descendants of, ordained priests forever<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=43'>Exo 28:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=3&verse=3'>Num 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=18&verse=1'>Num 18:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=23&verse=13'>1Ch 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=18'>2Ch 26:18</a><br/> Judges Israel in the absence of Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=14'>Exo 24:14</a><br/> Makes the golden calf<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32'>Exo 32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=40'>Act 7:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=21'>Deu 9:21</a><br/> Rod of, buds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=17&verse=13'>Num 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=4'>Heb 9:4</a><br/> Rod of, preserved<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=17&verse=13'>Num 17:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=4'>Heb 9:4</a><br/> Murmured against, by the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=5&verse=21'>Exo 5:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=10'>Exo 16:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=5'>Num 14:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=14&verse=10'>Num 14:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=11'>Num 16:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=41'>Num 16:41</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=2'>Num 20:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=16'>Psa 106:16</a><br/> Places pot of manna in the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=34'>Exo 16:34</a><br/> With Hur supports the hands of Moses during battle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=12'>Exo 17:12</a><br/> His benedictions upon the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9&verse=22'>Lev 9:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=6&verse=23'>Num 6:23</a><br/> Forbidden to mourn the death of his sons, Nadab and Abihu<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=6'>Lev 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=19'>Lev 10:19</a><br/> Intercedes for Miriam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=12'>Num 12:12</a><br/> Stays the plague by priestly intercession<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=48'>Num 16:48</a><br/> Jealous of Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=12&verse=1'>Num 12:1</a><br/> His presumption, when the rock is smitten<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=12'>Num 20:12</a><br/> Not permitted to enter Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=12'>Num 20:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?boo